    A[Organ Repositories] --> B[Own Site - Canonical]
    B --> C[Mastodon]
    B --> D[Discord]
    B --> E[Newsletter]
    B --> F[GitHub Pages]
    C --> G[Fediverse Network]
    D --> H[Community Servers]
    E --> I[Subscriber Inboxes]
    F --> J[Search Engines / RSS]`}
